imes have been attributed to Eric Rudolph? What efforts have been made to capture him and how has he eluded capture?"} {:experiment "D0730G", :topic "line item veto", :query "What has been the argument in favor of a line item veto? How has it been used?  How have US courts, especially the Supreme Court, ruled on its constitutionality?"} {:experiment "D0731G", :topic "Linda Tripp", :query "What role did Linda Tripp play in the Clinton/Lewinsky affair and the Ken Starr investigation?"} {:experiment "D0732H", :topic "Kenya education developments", :query "Kenya is attempting to raise its economic status. One approach is to raise the educational level of its population. What developments are there in this approach?"} {:experiment "D0733H", :topic "public programs at Library of Congress", :query "The Library of Congress is available to the public for research. What additional programs and attractions are available?"} {:experiment "D0734H", :topic "acupuncture treatment in U.S.", :query "It appears that acupuncture treatment is being increasingly accepted in the U.S. for medical problems. How is acupuncture being integrated into the American healthcare system and what are its applications?"} {:experiment "D0735H", :topic "reintroduction program for wolves in U.S.", :query "Note the current situation with the program to reintroduce endangered wolves. What problems exist and what are the prospects for success?"} {:experiment "D0736H", :topic "Oprah Winfrey TV show", :query "Note the various subjects and controversial incidents on Oprah's show 1998-2000."} {:experiment "D0737I", :topic "deep water exploration", :query "What is being learned from the study of deep water, seabeds, and deep water life? What equipment and techniques are used? What are plans for future related activity?"} {:experiment "D0738I", :topic "mining in South America", :query "What is the status of mining in central and South America?  Include obstacles encountered."} {:experiment "D0739I", :topic "after \"Seinfeld\"", :query "What became of the cast and others related to the \"Seinfeld\" TV series after it ended? What actions were taken by others in response to the show's closing?"} {:experiment "D0740I", :topic "round-the-world balloon flight", :query "Report on the planning, attempts and first successful balloon circumnavigation of the earth by Bertrand Piccard and his crew."} {:experiment "D0741I", :topic "day trader killing spree", :query "Give the background on Atlanta day trader Mark O. Barton's killing spree and the aftermath."} {:experiment "D0742J", :topic "John F. Kennedy, Jr., dies in plane crash", :query "Write an account of the sequence of events involving the Kennedy family during and following the plane crash that killed John F. Kennedy, Jr., his wife, and his sister-in-law."} {:experiment "D0743J", :topic "earthquakes in Western Turkey in August 1999", :query "Two massive earthquakes occurred in Turkey in 1999.  Describe the rescue efforts and the impact of the earthquakes on the economy, society, etc., in Turkey."} {:experiment "D0744J", :topic "organic food", :query "Describe the developments in the growth of the organic food industry, U.S. government efforts to set standards, and the public's attitude toward food (especially organic and genetically altered or biotech foods) in 1999 and 2000."} {:experiment "D0745J", :topic "OJ Simpson developments", :query "Give an account of the developments in the life of OJ Simpson in the years 1999 and 2000."})